notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: S.P. and R.P. designed the study. S.F. and C.F. selected the serum samples and conducted the analysis. M.J., L.L. and C.M.-P. were involved in nasal swab and serum collection related to the 2018 influenza outbreak. S.P., R.P., S.F., C.F., M.J., L.L. and C.M.-P. were involved in the results interpretation and manuscript preparation.
